00067 void CHPMultiDataDataTest::test_AlgParams()
00068 {
00069         ParameterNameValueTypeList params;

00071         CHPMultiDataData data;
00072 
00073         param.SetName(L"n1");
00074         param.SetValueText(L"v1");
00075         params.push_back(param);
00076 
00077         param.SetName(L"n2");
00078         param.SetValueText(L"v2");
00079         params.push_back(param);
00080 
00081         data.AddAlgParams(params);
00082 
00083         ParameterNameValueTypeList params_out = data.GetAlgParams();
00084         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(params_out.size() == 2);
00085         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it = params_out.begin();
00086         param = *it;
00087         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"n1");
00088         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"v1");
00089         ++it;
00090         param = *it;
00091         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"n2");
00092         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"v2");
